-------------------------------------------------------------------|\n    | The order of the branches is not important because all the branches of a parallel activity run at the same time. |\n\n3.  To configure each branch, see [Configure a parallel branch](configure-parallel-branch-workflow.md).\n\n\n\n\n\n","nodes":[{"pos":[4,718],"embed":true,"restype":"x-metadata","content":"# required metadata\n\ntitle: Configure a parallel activity in a workflow\ndescription: To configure a parallel activity, complete the following procedures in the workflow editor.\nauthor: sericks007\nmanager: AnnBe\nms.date: 06/20/2017\nms.topic: article\nms.prod: \nms.service: dynamics-ax-applications\nms.technology: \n\n# optional metadata\n\n# ms.search.form: \n# ROBOTS: \naudience: Application User, IT Pro\n# ms.devlang: \nms.reviewer: sericks\nms.search.scope: Core, AX 7.0.0, Operations, UnifiedOperations\n# ms.tgt_pltfrm: \nms.custom: 195753\nms.assetid: 6d0656df-b5af-4001-96e6-6f0fcc44d022\nms.search.region: Global\n# ms.search.industry: \nms.author: donaldc\nms.search.validFrom: 2016-02-28\nms.dyn365.ops.version: AX 7.0.0\n","nodes":[{"content":"Configure a parallel activity in a workflow","nodes":[{"pos":[0,43],"content":"Configure a parallel activity in a workflow","nodes":[{"content":"Configure a parallel activity in a workflow","pos":[0,43]}]}],"path":["title"],"extradata":"MT"},{"content":"To configure a parallel activity, complete the following procedures in the workflow editor.","nodes":[{"pos":[0,91],"content":"To configure a parallel activity, complete the following procedures in the workflow editor.","nodes":[{"content":"To configure a parallel activity, complete the following procedures in the workflow editor.","pos":[0,91]}]}],"path":["description"],"extradata":"MT"}],"header":"# required metadata\n","yml":true},{"pos":[726,769],"content":"Configure a parallel activity in a workflow","linkify":"Configure a parallel activity in a workflow","nodes":[{"content":"Configure a